title: Did the posters on the pop-bong van change the suspect incomprehensible after his arrest?
subtitle: Social media users predicted that something was bad for obvious changes in the post-Trump display on Cesar Sayuk's seized truck.
author: David Emery
vclaim: Photos and video of the suspect in the car bomb Cesar Seok during and after confiscation by the FBI reveal that some political posters on their windows have changed vaguely in this process.
